Comogenic Cycle - Virgin Birth - Mother Universe

The world generating spirit of father passes onto manifold
of earthly experience through a transforming medium -- 
the mother of the world.

She is personification of primal element named in Genesis. 
In hindu, she si female figure through whom self begot all 
creatures. 


in abstractly, she is world bounding frame, "space, time and 
causality" -- the shell of cosmic egg. 

original female fills world stage in the beginning, playing 
roles that are elsewhere assigned to female, she is virgin, 
because her spouse is invisible unknown. 


